298
00:28:12,860 --> 00:28:14,620
Close your eyes.

299
00:28:20,560 --> 00:28:22,500
Don't peek.

300
00:28:28,360 --> 00:28:29,900
Open your mouth.

301
00:28:36,940 --> 00:28:39,540
- Chocolate? 
 - A little snack won't fill you up.

302
00:28:39,540 --> 00:28:41,740
But it's better than nothing.

303
00:28:42,380 --> 00:28:44,740
Then, why didn't you bring it out last night?

304
00:28:44,740 --> 00:28:45,900
I was starving back then.

305
00:28:45,900 --> 00:28:47,940
