316
00:29:10,100 --> 00:29:12,280
Luckily, the water receded after the rain stopped.

317
00:29:12,280 --> 00:29:14,280
Did the water recede quickly?

318
00:29:24,400 --> 00:29:26,320
The water here came from seepage.

319
00:29:36,220 --> 00:29:37,580
This place is all soil.

320
00:29:37,580 --> 00:29:40,380
And there probably aren't many rocks underneath.

321
00:29:40,380 --> 00:29:43,040
That's why the water could seep through so fast.

322
00:29:44,640 --> 00:29:47,280
This cave goes deep.

323
00:29:48,780 --> 00:29:52,740
