324
00:29:52,740 --> 00:29:56,231
If it's all soil below, that means...

325
00:29:56,714 --> 00:29:58,180
- We can dig. 
 - Dig what?

326
00:29:58,180 --> 00:30:00,180
A path.

327
00:30:00,180 --> 00:30:01,980
A tunnel?

328
00:30:03,060 --> 00:30:04,600
How many years would that take?

329
00:30:04,600 --> 00:30:06,480
Are we really going to dig?

330
00:30:08,060 --> 00:30:09,780
Yes.

331
00:30:31,780 --> 00:30:33,560
Hello.

332
00:30:38,700 --> 00:30:40,280
