335
00:30:46,420 --> 00:30:49,820
Is this Jenny Cao's place?

336
00:30:50,840 --> 00:30:53,322
- You mean Jin Hua? 
 - Yes.

337
00:30:53,322 --> 00:30:56,505
- Yes, it is. 
 - Jenny! Jenny!

338
00:30:56,505 --> 00:30:59,265
