393
00:33:27,820 --> 00:33:29,900
Here. Soon the groom will receive the memorial tablet from here.

394
00:33:29,900 --> 00:33:31,700
After that, he can fetch the bride.

395
00:33:31,700 --> 00:33:33,300
- Memorial tablet? 
 - Yes.

396
00:33:33,300 --> 00:33:34,480
It's our tradition.

397
00:33:34,480 --> 00:33:37,040
There's an ancient memorial tablet kept by the eldest villager.

398
00:33:37,040 --> 00:33:41,000
For every wedding, a boy under seven fetches it from the elder's place.

399
00:33:41,000 --> 00:33:43,060
After that, he follows the gong bearer,

400
00:33:43,060 --> 00:33:44,580
circling the village with the tablet.

401
00:33:44,580 --> 00:33:46,180
Finally, it's presented to the groom.

402
00:33:46,180 --> 00:33:48,840
The newlyweds must honor the tablet before bowing to heaven and earth.

